                   platform Facebook. Here, higher activity of the
                   nucleus accumbens was associated with gaining
                   reputation on social media. In the present study, we
                   touched a related research field. We recorded the
                   actual Facebook usage of N = 62 participants on
                   their smartphones over the course of five weeks and
